{"tid":989894,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"直播買到黑心床墊　苦主：收到髒話都飆出來了","createTime":"2019-01-21T07:55:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T10:06:33.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bd1657566726146b2d1a7b637fb9e67024d056b4","tid":989894,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:55:57.000Z","msg":"臉書社團「爆怨公社」內一名網友日前看直播購買了一組1300元的雙人床墊，想要放在家中和室內，沒想到收到貨一拆開竟發現床墊凹凸不平，而且拉鍊還被縫死，將拉鍊拆開後立刻看到超噁心內裏，網友情緒瞬間爆炸，連髒話都飆出來。<br />\n這名苦主PO網說，當時收到貨後還請公公辛苦的幫忙搬到家裡，結果卻發現買到黑心床墊，問直播平台竟還回說：不知道廠商會這樣？雖然最後直播平台願意退款，但買到黑心床墊的網友的心情仍無法平復，沒想到有信用的直播平台還開發票，竟也會買到黑心商品。<br />\n其他網友見到PO文內容也說「太噁心了」、「這是垃圾場撿的吧」、「民國幾年了，台灣怎麼還有這麼黑心的廠商。」但也有網友說「這種東西還是實際現場購買比較安心！」<br />\n《蘋果》實地走訪該間位於新莊區三泰路的床墊製造工廠，只見鐵皮工廠大門敞開，內部已空無一物。隔壁工廠員工表示，這間公司已經搬走好幾個月了，且之前該工廠內有好幾家公司，並不清楚到底是生產什麼商品的。（突發中心張貴翔、黃子騰／新北報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190121/640_cdd917266b3b4ef37852d9455fa524d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190121%2F640_cdd917266b3b4ef37852d9455fa524d7.jpg&h=c040279a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190121/640_137ef420c1e2f08df99746f63bc296b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190121%2F640_137ef420c1e2f08df99746f63bc296b4.jpg&h=1aa34f20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190121/640_2cb660e6bff0cff209ff634f29d65ccd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190121%2F640_2cb660e6bff0cff209ff634f29d65ccd.jpg&h=e4c79e10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20190121/1504480/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20190121%2F1504480%2F&d=DzQ%2BdqR9z8afoqiyVUfjdcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=e946801a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2F20190121%2F1504480%2F&h=e289b469\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/20190121/1504480/</a>"},{"pid":"7e3115f8bfaac862ba372727ebfe2aea039c3425","tid":989894,"uid":13303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T09:04:28.000Z","msg":"都是支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf7461484a5d92ab1744f6a7486ca7d60f9a26e8","tid":989894,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T09:53:01.000Z","msg":"台灣不意外"},{"pid":"37848ac8946fca0a89a466a11d677bb8815f6040","tid":989894,"uid":119494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf7461484a5d92ab1744f6a7486ca7d60f9a26e8","tid":989894,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T09:53:01.000Z","msg":"台灣不意外"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T10:06:33.000Z","msg":"支那人"}]}